{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-10603/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-10603"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:06:03"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["extreme close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["overhead"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man salts a plate of asparagus."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10603/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-10603","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10603/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-10603"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10603/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10603/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10603/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10603/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10603/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10603/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10603/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10603/canvas/1/685b9c63-e8c3-412d-b7a8-bb479263ee99","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T18:54:47.981Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds’s application of a truly absurd amount of salt to his asparagus exemplifies the entanglement of tension and humor that pervades PTA’s films. Throughout <em>Phantom Thread</em>, desire is articulated by linking the consumption of food and sexual pleasure. Here, we see the dinner as a site of contestation for Reynolds and Alma’s relationship—Alma’s attempt to reframe the terms of their dynamic is met with Reynolds’s petty attempts to reassert the status quo.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10603/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:481.39358108108104,372.86528716216213,598.7521114864865,447.77660472972974"}}}]}]}]}